{"tid":1837944,"cid":31,"subCid":7,"title":"搭高鐵迎春花　人人都怕它","createTime":"2020-01-23T23:56:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-03T03:58:30.000Z","uid":182001,"like":414,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":68,"replies":[{"pid":"409fe67e3b8f01e095097e7daa32590bec7b3f31","tid":1837944,"uid":182001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T23:56:57.000Z","msg":"傻的嗎 ？ (武漢版)<br />\n原曲：迎春花<br />\n改詞：叮三分鐘<br />\n<br />\n搭高鐵傻的嗎　人人都怕它<br />\n去中國傻的嗎　隨時亡命獻中華<br />\n野味店傻的嗎　蝙蝠吃一打<br />\n信中國傻的嗎 如無防疫真可怕<br />\n<br />\n同胞衝關 肺炎惹起亂麻<br />\n同胞出現 武漢通報大話<br />\n相當閉翳 攔截困難<br />\n萬事注意 無牽掛<br />\n<br />\n戴口罩傻的嗎　人人搶購它<br />\n要封國傻的嗎　隨時亡命獻中華<br />\n過春節傻的嗎　咳聲每一家<br />\n信中國傻的嗎　傻人投共一樂也<br />\nLa... La... La... La..."},{"pid":"0f6c69f7f0e6b5f1eca1714784a93962739ee5e0","tid":1837944,"uid":45255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T23:58:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb0acf1f9807ca3cfde103df1f244648238a063e","tid":1837944,"uid":77191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T00:43:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9f9b4d0e3d5616a32997a0b09661de08b686b7f","tid":1837944,"uid":54524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T00:44:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3b42c90ad58439676373d88030ec8c5f454799f","tid":1837944,"uid":211727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T00:44:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"h